Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The historic War of the Best \Nin Marineford has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 years ago, in the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy met Ace for the \Nfirst time when he was 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Won't Run! Ace's Desperate \NRescue Operation!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's him, Porchemy-san!\N--He stole the money from us! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it easier for us \Nby coming here voluntarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were having a hard time \Nmaking your friend talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Porchemy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It kind of hurts. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what happens \Nwhen you mess with adults?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight you! Sabo, help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.33,0:05:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a sword! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he got the knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Porchemy-san, that kid...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I come to face someone, I won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?! You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! He's not like \Nthe thugs in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Enough playing \Naround! That's our money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to us peacefully, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must been possessed by \Nsome evil spirit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give the money back so you won't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have better plans for that money!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so reckless! \NWhy are you always like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm beaten by kids, I may \Nas well quit being a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll make sure you quit!\N--We'll make sure you quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:07:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the whole story, \NPorchemy. How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you honestly get beaten by kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Captain Bluejam... The money is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me! I don't \Neven want to see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who will get my money back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me we'll let \Nit go without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. We'll get it back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a bad habit, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When faced with a real \Npirate it's best to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have such a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't feel right. \NI liked the one I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:08:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a stupid mistake. \NThe Bluejam clan won't forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll come after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was scary! \NI thought I was gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying! Shut up! \NStop crying already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like cowards or people who cry a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You helped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You...!\N--Whoa, he's just being thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you cough it \Nup in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're kind of people who'd kill \Nwomen or kids without hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if I said anything... \Nyou wouldn't be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than dying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you wanna become my friend that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I give you a hard time until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you follow me this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have nobody else to trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go back to Windmill Village \Nand I don't like the mountain bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't follow you, I'd be all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being lonely is more \Npainful than getting hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa is all I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it easy for you when I'm around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's hard without me?\N--Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Gold Roger had a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that there isn't such a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be some kind of devil \Nwho'd be better off dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't like spoiled kids like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not spoiled! I'm strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong?! You're not strong \Nat all! You cry like a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever gotten hit by \Na spiky thing? I'm only 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I become your age - 10, I'll \Nstop crying and become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't cry even if I were \N7, stupid! I'm not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become stronger than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Shanks that I'd \Nbecome a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You? Become a pirate?\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No way!\N--Yes way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, by the way, I have a little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What? A problem?\N--Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam and the others will try to kill the \Nthree of us after this for sure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This forest that I've been living is close \Nto where they are - the Cove of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if they attack me when \NI fall asleep exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're gonna die.\N--Yeah, you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, huddle up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they wounded? They're all bandaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Boss! Boss! We have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? It's still early. What's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, Luffy... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, Luffy... Huh? Ace, Luffy... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... Luffy... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, Luffy, huh? Ace, Luffy, \Nhuh? Ace, Luffy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy! Who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still early - you're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come there is one more kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sabo! Hey, you must be Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo? I've heard your name before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? That makes it easier! Thank \Nyou for taking care of me from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Taking care"? Don't tell me \Nthat you're gonna stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't answer me with a fart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be kidding! I heard that \Nyou're a worthless brat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? I heard that you're \Na worthless old bag, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unnecessary information!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna look after one more brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that you're a good worthless \Nold bag because you can't refuse a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're a truly \Nmanly worthless old bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Truly manly"? I'm a woman! \NI'm not a gender bender!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, Luffy, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving you a place to stay! \NYou gotta get to work already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See ya!\N--See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! You stay here and do \Nsome laundry and clean the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ace, Sabo, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! What annoying brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forget to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're gone, the Bluejam \Nclan might come by so be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bluejam clan might come by? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we beat some of his crew up! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan sure is an understanding \Nworthless old bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still a worthless old bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus she's a mountain bandit \Nand her face is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, so you ate the Devil Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you can have this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind, Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what fruit did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum? Gum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for the ability to swim, \Nyour body turned to rubber? So crappy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not crappy! I can use \Na lot of unbeatable attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have such a fat mouth even \Nthough you can't catch a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body really is rubber! Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play with my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But rubber surely stretches \Nand shrinks and expands so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...maybe it's useful when you're fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! Oh yeah, I came \Nup with another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called "Gum-Gum Balloon"! I can \Ndeflect cannonballs and everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Can you do it for me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll do it just for \Nyou! Ace can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What is it?! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! You're getting bigger and bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon! See it?! It's cool, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think it's cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good for working off my meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, kick it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the unbeatable attack \Nthat will deflect cannonballs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you deflect my kick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait! You can't just eat and run!\N--Wait! You can't just eat and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastard!\N--You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take this!\N--Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what can I say? Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I almost got eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. You can have a lot \Nof crocodile meat for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I forgive you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna eat the crocodile already. \NI can't wait until dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! I wanna check something quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Did you find it?\N--Look carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that we moved the "pirate savings".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna check the Gray Terminal, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay. Why don't you go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't listen to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are hooligans from the city \Nand Bluejam's people everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that Bluejam got really frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! The kids that you're \Nlooking for are all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You can't run from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that they bought \Nover pops at the Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better lay low for a \Nwhile until things calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? We'll just fight if they find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true but we don't have \Nto look for trouble ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam... The kids made quite an enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that they're gonna find \Nthis place and come by pretty soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that we can defeat them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is the end of the Dadan family!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say goodbye to the \Nhumble-but-sweet mountain bandit's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to quit the mountain bandit \Nbusiness than to get exterminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We can't defeat them"? \N"Out of business"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic you guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you take pride in \Nbeing a mountain bandit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they come by,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can just hand Ace and \Nthe other two over to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, boss, how do we explain it to Garp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:22:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, Bluejam is not the kind of guy who \Nwill be satisfied by just handing them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just pretend that \Nwe don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, try it! We gotta practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, are Ace and Sabo \Nhere? Just spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Boss! Ace and the other two are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's close friend Sabo \Nstarted to live with them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after being forced to \Nleave the Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, Sabo, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These three soon began spending their time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fighting with wild animals in \Nthe mountain and in the jungle
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.52,0:23:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and with hooligans from the \Ncity and pirates at the cove.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the people at \Nthe center of the kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came to know their wrongdoing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The names of Luffy, Ace, and Sabo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.88,0:23:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gradually gain fame among \Nthe thugs in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.25,0:23:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, one day, the three \Nof them meet a certain boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That meeting would change \Ntheir destinies in a big way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To The Sea Someday! \NThe Pledge of the Three Brats!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
